{
  "name": "Workflow 4B \u2013 Checkout Validation Processor",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Workflow 4B \u2013 Checkout Validation Processor\n\nPolls CheckoutSubmissions every 1 minute for PENDING rows.\n\n**Validation checks (in order):**\n1. Cleaner match \u2014 cleanerIdFromForm must equal fixedCleanerId in CleaningJobs\n2. Clock-in exists \u2014 job status must be IN_PROGRESS\n3. Duration minimum \u2014 checkout must be \u2265 30 min after clock-in\n4. Duration maximum \u2014 checkout must be \u2264 6 hours after clock-in\n5. GPS radius \u2014 cleaner must be within 100m of property\n\n**On APPROVED:**\n- CheckoutSubmissions: processingStatus = APPROVED\n- CleaningJobs: status = COMPLETED, clockOutTimeUTC, gpsClockOut fields\n- Reservations: cleaningStatus = COMPLETED\n\n**On REJECTED:**\n- CheckoutSubmissions: processingStatus = REJECTED with reason\n- No other sheets updated\n\n**NOTE:** CheckoutSubmissions tab uses mode:name (update to gid once tab is created).",
        "height": 380,
        "width": 420,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "f0a1b2c3-d4e5-6789-abcd-000000000001",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-1420, 560]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
